<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title><%= product.title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('../partials/nav') %>
<h1><%= product.title %></h1>
<% if (product.status === 'blocked') { %><p class="errors">신고 누적으로 차단된 상품입니다 (본인에게만 표시).</p><% } %>
<% if (product.image_path) { %><img src="<%= product.image_path %>" alt="상품 이미지" style="max-width:100%"><% } %>
<p><%= product.description %></p>
<p>가격: <%= product.price %>원</p>
<p>판매자: <%= product.seller_username %></p>
<% if (isOwner) { %>
  <p><a href="/products/<%= product.id %>/edit">수정/삭제</a></p>
<% } else if (currentUser) { %>
  <p>
    <a href="/chat/<%= product.seller_id %>">판매자와 채팅</a>
    | <a href="/report?type=product&id=<%= product.id %>">상품 신고</a>
    | <a href="/report?type=user&id=<%= product.seller_id %>">판매자 신고</a>
  </p>
<% } %>
</body>
</html>
